:Brand: Dell, Manufacturer reference: DW 1550 :Dell Part: 555-BBQB, Manufacturer Part: 453T2 <small> *The ''Dell Wireless 1550 WLAN/BT Combo Half Mini-Card'' is one of the new wireless products that will :be introduced with the new series of Business Client & CSMB (E5/M14 family) notebook offerings. :One of the key commodities used in notebooks today is the wireless Ethernet communication devices. *The E5/M14 notebooks are coupled with new key features such as faster 802.11 AC wireless connectivity :and next generation WiFi, as well as Tri-Band wireless for supporting wireless docking and video (WiGig). </small> Supported models: Latitude 3330 (01- SKU:Latitude 3330) *Dell Wireless DW1550 - [[Broadcom]] BCM4352 (2T2R abgn/ac) :[14e4:43b1] - [1028:0017] PCI\VEN_14E4&DEV_43B1&SUBSYS_00171028 :[413c:8143] - BCM20702A1 combo (DW1550 Bluetooth 4.0 LE) *Dell Wireless DW1550 - driver for ASUS MB [http://forum.ixbt.com/topic.cgi?id=14:60603:836#836 Z87-DELUXE] :Wi-Fi: PCI\VEN_14E4&DEV_43B1&SUBSYS_00171028&REV_03 :BT: USB\VID_413C&PID_8143&REV_0112 BCM20702A0 {DW1550 Bluetooth 4.0 LE}
